        "body": "Goal: Make the local Node server the execution runtime\nStatus: open\n\nTasks in scope:\n1. Define the runtime graph contract\n2. Extract execution into a local runtime service\n3. Implement phase 1 executable node set\n4. Wire Twilite to run graphs against the local runtime\n5. Unify runtime logs, state, and failures in diagnostics\n6. Package the local runtime for development and install\n\nOpen questions:\n1. How do semantic graphs promote into executable graphs later?",
